1. Nadamo *se* da ćemo uspeti da rešimo ovaj problem. (We hope *to* be able to solve this problem.)
2. Ja se nadam *da* ćeš mi pomoći. (I hope *that* you will help me.)
3. Nadamo *se* da će vreme biti lepo za vikend. (We hope *that* the weather will be nice for the weekend.)
4. Oni *se* nadaju da će pobediti na sutrašnjoj utakmici. (They hope *to* win tomorrow's game.)
5. Nadam *se* da ćeš doći na moju rođendansku proslavu. (I hope *that* you will come to my birthday party.)
6. Ja se nadam *da* ćeš mi oprostiti zbog onog što sam uradio. (I hope *that* you will forgive me for what I did.)
7. Nadam *se* da će mi posao biti odobren. (I hope *that* my job will be approved.)
8. Nadao *sam se* da ćemo imati više vremena za odmor. (I had hoped *that* we would have more time for rest.)
9. Oni su se nadali *da* će dobiti nagradu za svoj rad. (They had hoped *that* they would receive an award for their work.)
10. Nadam *se* da ćemo se uskoro videti. (I hope *that* we will see each other soon.)